                                    <condition>Parchment stained and dirty, the edges are stained green in places. Several holes and tears in the parchment, many of the tears have been repaired with stitching, e.g. bottom outer corner on <locus from="84" to="84" scheme="folios"/>. On <locus from="133" to="133" scheme="folios"/> there is a tear through half of the leaf.</condition>
