                            <handDesc>
                                <handNote xml:id="hand-1">Gothic textualis.</handNote>
                            </handDesc>
                            <additions>
                                <p>
                                    <locus from="1r" to="1r" scheme="folios"/>
                                    <note>Top of page, black ink by a modern hand: <quote>10 RB Du</quote>; <quote>Kgl. Biblioth<hi rend="super">t</hi> 1845</quote>; below in brown ink: <quote>IHB</quote>.</note>
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <locus from="2v" to="2v" scheme="folios"/>
                                    <note>Bottom of page, in brown ink by medieval hand: <quote>Das buech gehertt schwester Elisabetha Luthenbergrrin</quote>.</note>
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <locus from="8r" to="223v" scheme="folios"/>
                                    <note>Occasional additions in the margins by at least one contemporary hand. The additions usually consist of corrections. On <locus from="110r" to="110r" scheme="folios"/> a longer addition has been made in the bottom margin.</note>
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <locus from="Note_1" to="Note_1" scheme="other"/>
                                    <note>Paper note with three lines of writing by an early modern hand placed between <locus from="152v" to="152v" scheme="folios"/> and <locus from="153r" to="153r" scheme="folios"/>. The content concerns st Agnes.</note>
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <locus from="170r" to="170r" scheme="folios"/>
                                    <note>Bottom margin, contemporary addition to the list of apostles.</note>
                                </p>
                            </additions>
                            <decoDesc>
                                <p>Main text in black ink, rubrics in red, capitals touched in red.</p>
                                <decoNote type="initials">
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="18r" to="18r" scheme="folios"/>: chapter puzzle initial D over 5 lines in red and blue. The initial is surrounded by flourishing in brown ink. <locus from="8r" to="223v" scheme="folios"/>: plain initials over 1-2 line alternating in blue and red. On <locus from="8r" to="8r" scheme="folios"/> and <locus from="18r" to="18r" scheme="folios"/> the initials have some flourishing in brown ink; on <locus from="32r" to="32r" scheme="folios"/> and <locus from="111v" to="111v" scheme="folios"/> flourishing in red ink.</p>
                                </decoNote>
                                <decoNote type="bookmarks">
                                    <p>
                                        <locusGrp>
                                            <locus from="14" to="14" scheme="folios"/>
                                            <locus from="31" to="31" scheme="folios"/>
                                            <locus from="126" to="126" scheme="folios"/>
                                            <locus from="154" to="154" scheme="folios"/>
                                            <locus from="178" to="178" scheme="folios"/>
                                            <locus from="183" to="183" scheme="folios"/>
                                            <locus from="205" to="205" scheme="folios"/>
                                        </locusGrp>: page marks in leather.</p>
                                </decoNote>
